{"tid":686357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新盤經紀圍毆　4個打1個","createTime":"2018-06-01T07:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T08:31:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b38d70f02133db07bc22849298181bb3e0c3dc","tid":686357,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407779&d=JnLVKeEM%2FheA9YYMrJKQb4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=e186bad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407779&h=e7122faf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407779</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月01日 <br />\n<br />\n新盤經紀圍毆　4個打1個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180601/large/a1203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180601%2Flarge%2Fa1203a.gif&h=91413d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■嘉熙售樓處外昨有白衣男子被多人追打。讀者提供短片截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔新盤售樓廠發生疑似代理打交事件。昨晚新盤嘉熙位於荃灣嘉達環球中心的售樓處，有四名疑似地產經紀圍毆一人，其中一人先以掌推，把對方推埋牆角，及後三人一衝而上，該穿白恤衫男子隨即倒地並以雙手護頭，追打者連環拳狂打倒地男的頭部，另一名穿黑衣男子對着倒地男頭部大踢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉事樓盤明開售<br />\n<br />\n報料人士表示，上述男子疑似經紀，但影片內未見當事人佩戴任何代理行名牌。警方表示昨晚接到報案，一名31歲姓楊男子稱被三至四人襲擊，已送院接受檢查。據悉倒地男子為其中一間大型代理行員工，肩膀嚴重瘀傷，神志清醒。警方暫列糾紛案處理。地監局發言人表示會了解事件，持牌人如被證實在進行地產代理工作期間干犯涉及暴力案件，有機會被監管局紀律處分包括撤銷牌照。<br />\n<br />\n涉事樓盤為大埔白石角嘉熙，屬嘉華國際旗下，將於明日首度開售238伙。該盤上周六起收票，昨晚8時截票，市場消息指項目截收逾8,000票，以首批238伙計超額認購32.6倍。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳寶恩  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n街道清潔工拒調職遭逼走　入稟勝訴<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n康文署實名制防「炒場」"},{"pid":"a9642b1656c9a5701a94dc218779cdb619b656ae","tid":686357,"uid":70429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"餓狗搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534efa432b5bbd7fef28fb06613a7ea8399d5817","tid":686357,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"警方暫列糾紛案處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3ab52de9cda574dbc147c7966db1126976825a","tid":686357,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"鴻運當頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dedc0a7177dd9de4d9cd89d1a82f506c794e7e2","tid":686357,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:48:57.000Z","msg":"糾紛案?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/news/transform/20160209/5xWK-fxpfhzk9148975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fnews%2Ftransform%2F20160209%2F5xWK-fxpfhzk9148975.jpg&h=dcc20253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dbdf01ae614f0f44c1fae145e43fa309c45679c","tid":686357,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"喺呢幢大廈返工，每逢有新盤都好期待睇倒佢地打交，或者成班喪屍咁衝埋去擋住啲車，拉實車門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3870dadae3811685480941ef28f8df4c842b7a","tid":686357,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dbdf01ae614f0f44c1fae145e43fa309c45679c","tid":686357,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"喺呢幢大廈返工，每逢有新盤都好期待睇倒佢地打交，或者成班喪屍咁衝埋去擋住啲車，拉實車門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"好想一個人去挑佢地機....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n走埋去~今日開單未呀?!"},{"pid":"de5869181d8f1817cebb